WEBVTT

00:09:29.046 --> 00:09:30.732
And we're all walking on this path,

00:09:30.756 --> 00:09:33.941
and we're pulling these thickets
out of the way, and these thorns,

00:09:34.346 --> 00:09:36.506
making it easier for the ones
coming after us.

00:09:36.530 --> 00:09:40.561
It turns out, parenting
has a lot more to do with landscaping.

00:09:41.204 --> 00:09:42.354
And learning.

00:09:42.931 --> 00:09:44.131
More than teaching.

00:09:46.201 --> 00:09:48.796
And the best thing to do
is to show up for class.

00:09:49.622 --> 00:09:53.328
Be present is what I learned
as a stay-at-home dad.

00:09:54.190 --> 00:09:56.348
And let your presence be a gift.

00:09:56.372 --> 00:09:57.522
(Video) Shh.

00:09:57.952 --> 00:10:01.674
(Door unlocking)